// duplicates zdoom's lock list, modified to include chex quest keys. two vers.
// the SIMPLIFIED LOCKDEFS: these are included with the patch mod as-released.
// intended to replace chex quest's own LOCKDEFS with a more widely compatible
// set of locks - allowing use of all key types in all relevant lock types.
// the EXTENDED LOCKDEFS: released in a separate modder's resource package.
// based on doom's default locks, but extended with distinct entries for both
// chex quest keys and for heretic's prism keys. the EXTENDEDs were actually
// made first, then SIMPLIFIED so that all doom and chex keys are equivalent.

// setting up LANGUAGE entries for all of these is gonna be annoying...
// TODO: finalize advanced locks into modder resource and create simple locks

